description:
7th Legion from Microprose   

This is an RTS which was great in it's day. Unfortunately it never was rebuilt or patched(to my knowledge) to work on any other OS then Win '95 and Win '98.

However:
It does work , I got an old Win '98 machine 'lying around' for such an occasion.
It may well work by right clicking the Games exe and changing the compatability mode in
other OSs.

